				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-T%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/B%E1%BA%A1ch-H%E1%BA%A1c-Th%C3%B4ng-Th%C3%A1nh-qu%C3%A1n-chung-k%C3%BD/poem-Ou4K9qLcQmcRi8Smy9ITig">Bạch Hạc Thông Thánh quán chung ký - 白鶴通聖觀鐘記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-T%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-ZsqkhSzeSzEGkDGlaqk-Iw">Hứa Tông Đạo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thu-C%E1%BA%A9n/B%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91ao-ca/poem-xSg8AKrPyb-rb8BmHfyHpg">Bảo đao ca - 寶刀歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thu-C%E1%BA%A9n/author-X-40K1XlrcoKqxDGwb5eHg">Thu Cẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/C%E1%BA%A3nh-binh-%C4%91%E1%BA%A3m-tr%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-mSh_HSbsZEjm6DXfP6hjEQ">Cảnh binh đảm trư đồng hành - 警兵擔豬同行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/L%E1%BA%A1c-th%E1%BA%A7n-ph%C3%BA/poem-ylYQnboi4bp_70hzYu0a0Q">Lạc thần phú - 洛神賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Lai-T%C3%A2n/poem-2lXfDKw50qDnitf97NoG4w">Lai Tân - 來賓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/L%C3%A2m-chung-di-chi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-I86uGQtK3uDAayDqWSRvWw">Lâm chung di chiếu - 臨終遺詔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-sMXrZTDvW5uflSvv6NTMXQ">Lý Nhân Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Ph%C3%B9-dung-n%E1%BB%AF-nhi-lu%E1%BB%B5/poem-R9STBdCyvV6_VYrjugG5yQ">Phù dung nữ nhi luỵ - 芙蓉女兒誄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%